# Burn & Build — one repo

Repo: **`pwa-burn-and-build`** (this workspace)

**Product:** Brand-new **desktop web application** on burnandbuilddiet.com — not the old phone/PWA daily app.

| Path | Host | Role |
|------|------|------|
| `landing/` | burnandbuilddiet.com (GitHub Pages) | Marketing CTAs → questionnaire |
| `questionnaire/` | `/questionnaire/` | Intake steps → save plan → checkout handoff |
| `createyourfoodplan/` | `/createyourfoodplan/` | Plan-ready screen + Stripe paywall ($149 per program) |
| `program-report/` | `/program-report/` | Deliverable — projections, plan/servings |
| `mealplanner/` | `/mealplanner/` | Menu planner + Print Assistant (desktop) |
| `server/` | Render (`program-creator`) | API + SQLite — programs, per-program payment |
| `myplan/` | `/myplan/` | **Legacy phone app** — daily logging; not the desktop funnel |

**Desktop user flow:**
```
Landing → questionnaire → Stripe (per program) → program-report → mealplanner
```

Each new program requires its own Stripe checkout. Access is per `programId`, not lifetime per email.

**Deploy site:** push to `main` (paths in `.github/workflows/deploy-landing.yml`) → GitHub Pages.

**Hardkor Diet landing** merge tracker: `docs/LANDING-MERGE.md`. **Signal+** is a separate product.
